Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.28,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:23.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:30.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:40.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,140.389)}The Blood-Sucking Mosquilas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}Versus the Two Riders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Capable of draining not just the blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:54.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but all fluids from the human body,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:58.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the terrifying cyborg Mosquilas\Nwas Shocker's newest weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth, Mosquilas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Erect a new Shocker base.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your target is Katsuura Port\Nin the southern Kii Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kumano is at the center of the east\Nside of Yoshino-Kumano National Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy views of the Kuroshio\NCurrent in the Kumano-nada Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and beautiful green mountains."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye to those smoggy skies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't Nachi Falls\Nthe tallest waterfall in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They have that special candy there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Choco, are you talking about food again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want a soak in those\NKatsuura hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to you talk, like it's a vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going there to play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We're hunting bugs\Nfor our summer homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\3c&H3637C2&}Welcome\N{\3c&HFFB700&}Nachi-Katsuura \NTourism Department
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, almost there! A little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, there we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're growing like a weed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks for coming.\N- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All around there is Katsuura Port.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where the hot springs all bubble up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as grand a view as I'd imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to forget about Shocker\Nwhen you're in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know they'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This should make things very interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a view!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! You can't\Nsee this stuff in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of rhino\Nand stag beetles, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's climb a little higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Mr. Hongo to see this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But I dunno where we'll find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask that monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a question for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it... you're Shocker, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why aren't you guys eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two have been out for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be heading\Nback to eat around now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they got lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why aren't you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki and Mitsuru haven't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good. Naoki was with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just thinking\Nof going to look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have our clerk guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Naoki's hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We should split up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go this way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen two boys pass this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why yes, I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's the clerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the scream we heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Shocker was behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll do the same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay together, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. He got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I got hold of some information that\NShocker was sending its cyborg
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,created deep in the Amazon,\NMosquilas, to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here for summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't expecting\NShocker to show up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to establish a base\Nhere in the southern Kii Peninsula,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with access to the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki and the others are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive indeed, Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You tracked us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the children die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:48.39,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him, Mosquilas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've killed Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the entrance to their base...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigate the plunge pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Find Ichimonji Hayato's\Nbody and bring it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could they have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to pray to the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy a shrine fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us find the boys safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Those whom you seek are near.\NWait and they shall arrive."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got best luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for boys\Nabout ten years of age?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us where they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There were two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I found them collapsed in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're caring for them\Nin the great hall there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the girls to our underground base!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive as ever, Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he sniffed us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Mosquilas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone saw a monk\Nlead three girls in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the look of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've showed yourself... Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to transform and your friends die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have all five of them in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you. Come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boiling hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We've awaited your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going\Nto do to these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to save them,\Nlet Mosquilas feed upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Mosquilas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... it's time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, don't resist, or the children die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who turned it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn it back on at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Kill him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, get them to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hang in there.\N- I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, I'm going to join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... this isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's heading for Dorokyo Gorge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosquilas... you won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Knee Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:29.44,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:32.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:40.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:47.33,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:58.16,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:01.53,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:12.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.53,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:23.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:30.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:33.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:41.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.51,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:55.72,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:02.89,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:06.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:10.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:20.03,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:24.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:28.23,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kamen Riders...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will establish a Shocker base\Non the southern Kii Peninsula!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have yet more tricks in store.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Siomaneking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See the Kamen Riders dead at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:51.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi and Ichimonji Hayato had\Ndefeated the blood-sucking monster Mosquilas,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:54.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and stopped Shocker's\Nawful plan in its tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:59.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker wasn't finished yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:03.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,as it sent a monster called Siomaneking\N to the southern Kii Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:06.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.88,Cont,,0,60,155,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(290.175,272.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:16.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next monster that I, Ambassador Hell,\Nwill send in is Siomaneking!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:20.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He'll use the deadly foam that he shoots\Nfrom his mouth to melt down both Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:24.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I will create an underwater Shocker\Ncity no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:30.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, tune in next week for "Defeat It, Double Riders!!\NSiomaneking."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,700.389)}Double Riders!! Siomaneking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(573,444)}Defeat It
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:50.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:57.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:24:01.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:05.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:09.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:12.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blood-Sucking Mosquilas\NVersus the Two Riders